# Scripts directory
# Standalone Python scripts for pipeline steps

# Recommended scripts:
#   data_generator.py           — synthetic data generation using Faker
#   data_cleaning.py            — cleaning and validation routines
#   eda.py                      — automated EDA and summary statistics
#   segmentation.py             — RFM + KMeans customer segmentation
#   cohort_analysis.py          — cohort retention analysis
#   revenue_analysis.py         — revenue trends and forecasting
#   report_generator.py         — automated PDF/HTML report generation
